Title: Lykke til, Isak
Actors: Tarjei Sandvik Moe, Ulrikke Falch, Lisa Teige, Iman Meskini
Plot: Isak has to hide the drugs belonging to him, Jonas, Mahdi and Magnus at Eva's party when the police arrive, and he struggles to get it back. The first year girl Emma, shows interest in Isak. Isak joins the school revue group.
